{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"143be5a4eb","title":"给张曙时的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84608d00aa","index":0,"year":1947,"month":11,"day":18,"articleId":"143be5a4eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dde53d9cd2","type":"paragraph","text":"给张曙时的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"143be5a4eb"},{"id":"7091a97720","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年11月18日）曙时同志：十月十七日来示读悉。法律工作是中央新设领导工作的一个部门，兄及诸同志努力从事于此，不算“闲居”。将来时局开展，出到外面工作，自属必要。目前则在激烈战争中，年老的人出去，似乎尚非其时。法律本于人情，收集各解放区实际材料，确是必要的。关于宪草的意见，托王谢二同志转达，不整。贴体粗安，承问极感，大寒尚望珍费敬候起居健吉！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"143be5a4eb"},{"id":"d2ed8c17b7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"143be5a4eb"},{"id":"0e43b35349","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十八日il张晒时（1884-1971），江苏唯宁人。当时任中共中央法律委员会委员。2","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"143be5a4eb"}],"page":{"id":"bc83063c69","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"143be5a4eb","start":405,"end":405}}}},"__N_SSG":true}